New Movies on Netflix February 2017 33 New Movies and TV Shows to Watch on Netflix in February January 25, 2017 Share This Link Copy What’s Your Reaction? Thanks for your reaction Don’t forget to share this with your friends! ← Use Arrows Keys → 1 33 New Movies and TV Shows to Watch on Netflix in February 
Netflix just released its new titles for the month of February, and it's loaded with original movies and shows like White Nights and Stronger Than the World . Not only is Drew Barrymore 's highly anticipated zombie series, Santa Clarita Diet , set to release next month, but there are also some nostalgic gems on the list as well. Take a look to figure out what you'll be watching over the next few weeks! Related:
